-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style=''font-size: 24px; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>Why we are collection information and use?</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">We are collecting information about the user for a better experience, while using our service. For this maybe we need certain personally information. The Information, which are requested from us will not be retrained on your device and will not collected by us in any way.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">The app doesnt use for now third party services that may collect information used to identify you.&nbsp; It can be changed without giving noticed and if you use the service you agree with that. Because of this please visit our Privacy and Policy many times.</span></span></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style=''font-size: 24px; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>Log Data</span></span><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal"><span style=''font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>We want to inform you that whenever you use our service, in case of an\r\nerror or version incompatibility oft he app and the device, that we collect your\r\ndate for taking information (through third party products) on you device called\r\nLog Data. Those Log data may include information such as your device operating\r\nsystem version, internet protocol ("IP") address and the device name. Date and\r\nTime is too visible in the log data.&nbsp;</span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Cookies</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal"><span style=''font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>In this section we would give you some information about the cookies.\r\nCookies are small amount of data which will be saved on you devices internal\r\nmemory. This ware sent to you browser from the websites that you visit.&nbsp; We dont use directly cookies but the app may\r\nuse third party code and libraries that use "cookies" for improve their\r\nservices. While using a browser you can accept this our refuse these cookies.\r\nWhen you first time visit a website, you would be asked bye the devices if you\r\nwant to save cockies. In this case you can agree or disagree.</span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style=''font-size: 24px; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>Service Providers</span></span><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">For updating and developing the app we need sometimes third-party companies and individual due to&nbsp; the following reasons:</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To make the use oft he app easier.</span></span></li><li style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Companies, which helping use while programming and updating</span></span></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">We have to inform&nbsp; users of our service, that these companies or third parties have access to your personal information. Only when they get a job from ous they have acces to you data too. Which means that the third-parties only use your data for developing phase. However, they are obligated not to disclose or use the information for any other purpose.</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b>E-mail contact</b></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 18px;">If you contact us via the provided e-mail address, the data you provide will be used to process your request. The specification of the data is necessary for processing and answering your inquiry - without their provision we can not answer your inquiry or at best only to a limited extent.</span><br><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 18px;">Legal basis for this processing is in the presence of a consent Art. 6 para. 1 lit. a GDPR.</span><br><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 18px;">The legal basis for the processing of the data transmitted in the course of sending an e-mail is Article 6 (1) lit. f DSGVO.</span><br><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span><br><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 18px;">The data will be deleted as soon as it is no longer necessary to achieve the purpose of its collection. For the personal data sent by e-mail, this is the case when the respective conversation with the user has ended. The conversation ends when it can be inferred from the circumstances that the matter in question has been finally clarified.</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style=''font-size: 24px; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>Security oft he data and information</span></span><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">In this case we have to speak about the security of collected data and information. We don`t publish any kind of information about you. But sure internet and same protocols&nbsp; are&nbsp; not secure for 100% and because of this we are working everytime for security and realibility, but we can not gurantee its absolute security.</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style=''font-size: 24px; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>Links to Other Sites</span></span><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''><span style="font-size: 18px;">On our site you can find other links from other sites. If you click on them, you will be directed tot hat site. Note that these externel sites are not operated by us. Because of this please review the Privacy Policy of these websites. We don`t have any control over other sites and because this you should review the Privacy and Policy of these sites for prodecting you from miss understanding.&nbsp; Like we say before, we are not responsible for other sites.</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Childrens Privacy</span></span><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Our Service do not address anyone under the age of 15, because of this we do not knowingly collect personaly identifiable information from children under 15. When we see that there is data from a child under 15, we will remove it immediately from our service. And if you are parent of a child, which send us their data please contact us to take actions.</span></span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"></span></p><p><span style=''font-family: "Times New Roman", serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;''>Updating this Privacy Policy</span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style=''font-size: 18px; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>We will update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Because of this, thus who use our service should visit the page periodically for sean any changes. The updated Privacy Policy is effective after we are publishing them on this site.</span></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style=''font-size: 24px; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''>Contact Us</span></span><span style=''font-size: 13pt; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;''></span></p><p></p><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 19.9733px;">For any question or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at support@niontv.app</span></p><p class="p2" style=''margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 